    "title": "京东时尚相关类目个人/个体店铺招商激励政策（2026.3.1-2026.5.31）",
    "followRuleId": "1338687221000028160",
    "content": "<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">为鼓励商家在京东开放平台积极经营，特制定激励政策，具体内容如下：</span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">一、参与商家</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年3月1日起在京东开放平台完成入驻，并经营指定类目的个人/个体店铺。（注：以店铺维度考核）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">具体一级类目范围限定如下：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">运动户外、服饰内衣、母婴、箱包皮具、钟表眼镜、珠宝首饰、鞋靴、奢侈品</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：运动户外一级类目限芭蕾舞袜、羽毛球袜、篮球袜、瑜伽袜、芭蕾舞袜、运动袜、足球袜、瑜伽袜、户外袜、乒乓球袜等三级类目参与；母婴一级类目限儿童袜、儿童配饰、儿童内裤等三级类目参与。</span></em></span></p>\n<h1 style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">二、激励政策</span></strong></span></h1>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励周期：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2026</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年3月1日00：00至2026年5月31日23：59（以下称为&ldquo;考核期&rdquo;）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、激励规则：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）激励模式：以销售 NET GMV（计算方式详见3、数据口径）为基础进行考核。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）返还模式：按考核期考核，并按周期整体达标档位发放至商家京准通账户。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）激励、返还金额以京东系统确认为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、数据口径：</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）销售 GMV口径：为实收 NET GMV，即考核期内店铺内下单，且在2026年6月8日之前完成的订单产生的GMV【须剔除退货、未确认收货，取消订单、虚拟商品订单，刷单等风控订单、使用优惠券金额的订单等】，考核周期结束后，次月进行数据计算。其中销售GMV剔除站外投放部分。如有异常交易（例如刷单等）则不予发放。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）销售类目口径：<strong>仅统计店铺在一级类目运动户外、服饰内衣、母婴、箱包皮具、钟表眼镜、珠宝首饰、鞋靴、奢侈品下产生的销售情况。</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><em><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：运动户外一级类目限芭蕾舞袜、羽毛球袜、篮球袜、瑜伽袜、芭蕾舞袜、运动袜、足球袜、瑜伽袜、户外袜、乒乓球袜等三级类目参与；母婴一级类目限儿童袜、儿童配饰、儿童内裤等三级类目参与。</span></em></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、其它说明</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1）已享受平台特殊费率的订单所产生的GMV均计入本政策进行达成考核，但不再给予特殊费率订单所产生gmv的本政策下返利。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2）此政策实施期间不与其他新商激励政策同享。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3）激励周期内，若商家中途关店则激励终止。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">5</span></strong><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、具体返利政策：（0.6%交易服务费另行单独收取，GMV单位：人民币元）</span></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">注：店铺ID归属于京喜事业部下，具体店铺归属请咨询各店铺/类目运营，政策考核期内数据最终以平台数据为准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（1） 返还激励：以销售 GMV为基础进行考核，按照商品挂靠类目扣点做激励返还，激励支付形式为广告现金。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（2） 广告红包激励：以销售 GMV为基础进行考核，满足奖励周期内的销售GMV门槛即可获得对应广告红包奖励。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">（3） 广告红包使用说明：</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">政策奖金池600万(如遇上限，按店铺报名先后顺序发放)</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">②</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">红包金额向下取整，如1000.6元，发放1000元</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">③</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">使用范围：全站营销、快车通用（限制使用类目同限定商家参与类目）</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">④</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">有效期：到账后60天内，红包过期作废不予退还</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">⑤</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">消耗逻辑：红包需搭配现金按照1：1配比使用</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 2; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">⑥</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">发放逻辑：发放至广告投放现金消耗最高的京准通账号</span></span></p>\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" style=\"width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; line-height: 2;\" border=\"1\" width=\"100%\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.46%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">考核期</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.72%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">奖励门槛</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.1%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"21%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励1</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.72%; background: #DC1623; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\" align=\"center\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><strong><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: white;\">激励2</span></strong></span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.46%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位1</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞10W</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 21.1%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" rowspan=\"5\" width=\"21%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">技术服务费全返（广告现金形式）</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包10000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.46%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位2</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞20W</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包30000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.46%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位3</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">＞30W</span></span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 32.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"32%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">广告红包60000元</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 19.46%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"19%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">考核档位4</span></p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width: 26.72%; padding: .75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt;\" width=\"26%\">\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm 0cm 8pt; line-height: 115%; font-size: 11pt; font-family: 等线;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10pt;\"><span style=\"line-height: 115%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">NETGMV</span><span sty